Activity: A1 – Discover security concepts used on campus

Objective
The goal of this activity is to observe and analyse security concepts used on campus.

Method
I walked around campus and identified security measures such as CCTV cameras and access card doors.

Findings
I discovered the following security implementations:
1. CCTV cameras
2. Student access cards
3. Human security guards
4. Network login authentication to access Unifi

Security Principle
These systems support confidentiality, integrity, and availability.

Evidence


Reflection
This activity helped me understand how security concepts are applied in real environments.
